---
import V3InteriorLayout from '../../layouts/V3InteriorLayout.astro';
---

<V3InteriorLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  eyebrow="Legal"
  description="How mayafourteen.com handles visitor data: analytics, cookies and newsletter subscriptions."
  hasEsSibling
>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>

  <h2>Who we are</h2>
  <p>
    This website is operated by Maya Fourteen. For any privacy question, contact
    <a href="mailto:hello@mayafourteen.com">hello@mayafourteen.com</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    We use Google Analytics to understand, in aggregate and anonymous form, how this site is
    visited: pages viewed, country of origin, device type. Analytics cookies are only set
    after you accept them in the consent notice. If you decline, no analytics cookies are
    stored. You can change your choice at any time by clearing this site's data in your
    browser.
  </p>

  <h2>Newsletter</h2>
  <p>
    If you subscribe to the newsletter, your email address is stored with Brevo, our email
    service provider, and used only to send you the updates you signed up for. Subscription
    uses double opt-in: you are only added after confirming through the email we send you.
    Every message includes an unsubscribe link, and unsubscribing removes you from the list.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by
    writing to <a href="mailto:hello@mayafourteen.com">hello@mayafourteen.com</a>. We do not
    sell or share personal data with third parties beyond the service providers named above.
  </p>

  <h2>External links</h2>
  <p>
    This site links to external platforms (YouTube, Instagram, SoundCloud, Spotify and others).
    Their privacy practices are governed by their own policies.
  </p>
</V3InteriorLayout>

<style>
  .updated {
    font-size: 0.85em;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-top: 1.8em;
    margin-bottom: 0.4em;
    font-size: 1.35em;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
